      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ADHANA MADI (7) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 2 lengths away in third (39.70) behind Bandit Daryl at Murray Bridge. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Racing well and deserves a win. ADHANA TORI (1) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 10 lengths into third (43.89) at this track in a Special conditions race over 730m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can measure up. LOOSE MOOSE (5) produced a modest effort most recently when eighth at this track over 530m behind Victa Krev (31.54) in a Special conditions race. Worth following up. ZENVO YOYO (3) is worth including.",
